value: Breeds on Branco Island and Cima, Rombos Islands, Cape Verde Islands. Not distinguishable at sea from hypoleuca. Specimens have been found off the Atlantic coast of North America, and one recently in the Netherlands.
refer: Peter's Checklist of the Birds of the World

value: islets of Branco, Ilheu de Cima, Boavista and Maio (Cape Verde Is., s Macaronesia, w of nw Africa)
